"产生了分歧。现在他们又不情愿地被卷入了联邦与叛军的战争。"

#: src-ru/data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber:1186
msgid ""
"data/events_zoltan.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"START_BEACON_ZOLTON\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
